Package com.swagfish.tictactoe.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AlreadyOverException
    The AlreadyOverException exception is thrown when a play is trying to be made but the game has finished.
    InvalidTicTacToeSizeException
    The InvalidTicTacToeSizeException exception is thrown when map is trying to be made with an invalid size.
    NoWinnerException
    The NoWinnerException exception is thrown when there is no winner found, but the game is over.
    OutOfBoundsException
    The OutOfBoundsException exception is thrown when a play is trying to be made but the square is out of the map.
    SquareOccupiedException
    The SquareOccupiedException exception is thrown when a play is trying to be made but the chosen square is occupied.
